<p begin="00:05:50.080" end="00:05:53.900" style="s2">merkwürdig</p>
<p begin="00:05:52.560" end="00:05:58.210" style="s2">grob</p>
<p begin="00:05:53.900" end="00:05:58.210" style="s2">[Musik]</p>
<p begin="00:05:58.479" end="00:06:01.479" style="s2">grob</p>
<p begin="00:06:01.560" end="00:06:11.319" style="s2">[Musik]</p>
<p begin="00:06:05.400" end="00:06:11.319" style="s2">mir dauerte ungefähr 5 Jahre als ich</p>
