<p begin="00:07:10.610" end="00:07:27.300" style="s2">[Musik]</p>
<p begin="00:07:24.360" end="00:07:30.439" style="s2">[Applaus]</p>
<p begin="00:07:27.300" end="00:07:30.439" style="s2">[Musik]</p>
<p begin="00:07:32.440" end="00:07:38.840" style="s2">ich war zurückgeholt physisch</p>
